snippet.title: Playmobil The Explorers Hidden Temple with T-Rex Dinosaurs toy unboxing || Keith's Toy Box
snippet.description:
Join the Explorers as they embark on a new adventure on Dino Island with the Hidden Temple with T-Rex. Once you discover the temple, use the ancient structure as your research base before heading out to explore the island with the help of the secret map. Simply rub the map to reveal a hidden path where X marks the spot! When back at the base, protect the team from the unfriendly T-Rex or enemy explorers with the functioning laser gun (batteries included)! The
working temple gate also helps keep unwanted visitors out. Beware of that T-Rex! His movable arms, legs, and jaw allow for realistic motion and make him one intimidating dino! Use the functioning pulley to bring needed equipment up to the top floor. Kids can also use the included UV flashlight (1 x AAA battery required) to reveal cool glow-in-the dark features, such as with the ruin’s crystal eyes, jungle plant, and more! Set also includes the full Explorers team – Nick, Emma, and Will, their pet dog Sammy, T-Rex, laptop, camera, gold statue, microscope, backpacks, storage containers, hiking equipment, and lots of other accessories.

Available at Amazon
https://www.amazon.com/PLAYMOBIL®-Hidden-Temple-T-Rex-Building/dp/B0766D7R7L/?tag=thewanfulworo-20

More Dinosaurs and Jurassic World videos at

snippet.title: Love to Hug Elmo Plush Sesame Street Toy Unboxing
snippet.description:
Join us for a Love to Hug Elmo Sesame Street Toy Unboxing! We love Sesame Street toys and we’re so happy that Sesame Street has  been on for 50 years and counting. The Love to Hug Elmo plush toy is so cute and cuddly and Christian was so happy because Elmo is his favorite Sesame Street character. It’s very special to be able to share a show I loved as a child with my kids. And we are big Sesame Street collectors, especially Christian’s older brother who has autism and  lives and breathes all things Sesame Street. We hope you enjoy this video and don't forget to smile! 😊

#LoveToHugElmo #SesameStreetToys #KidsToys

snippet.title: TRANSFORMERS ROBOTS IN DISGUISE COMBINER FORCE TOY UNBOXING WAVE 12 SOUNDWAVE STRONGARM TRICKOUT
snippet.description:
NEW! Transformers more than meets the eye! Its hyper vault Soundwave as a cool 3 step Transformers robots in disguise changer. Soundwave is one bad decepticon and so much fun to transformer and play with. In this video we unbox two Transformers the new wave 12 3 step charger Soundwave and the combiner force Strongarm and Trickout. We transform them and show you all the really cool things about each of the toys in our toy review. Here is what harbro has to say about the new Soundwave hyper vault. Experience the excitement of conversion in three awesome steps, with Transformers: Robots in Disguise Combiner Force 3-Step Changer figures. In order to convert this 3-Step Changer Soundwave figure from robot to tank, swing the arms up and over and flip the legs behind the head in a smooth Hyper-Vault motion. Imagine charging into battle with figures that change modes in 3 steps! Scan the Decepticon shield on this figure to unlock a token in the mobile app. We love the Transformers Robots in Disguise game on toytimetv! Soundwave is the ultimate spy, capable of locating any enemy. The treacherous signal stealer can detect any Autobot transmission and mask his own signature to avoid detection. The Autobots may not realize the Decepticon has targeted them until it’s too late. who are the Transformers robots in disguise? When new Decepticons appear, Optimus Prime summons Bumblebee and gives him the task of saving Earth. To help him, the veteran Autobot assembles a rogue team of young bots to capture the new enemies. The new Autobot recruits include a rebel "bad boy," an elite guard cadet, a bombastic dinobot and a hyperactive mini-con. The recruits provide a challenge for Bumblebee because, while each is a fully capable hero, they are inexperienced when it comes to working as a team. So Bumblebee has to learn how to balance his role as a leader of the new squad with his job of fighting evil forces as he works to complete the mission. We love the Transformers cartoon on cartoon network. Transformers more than meets the eye! Be sure and subscribe for more!

This machinery develops the kid’s logic, imagination and motor skills. Also visual perception and memory

snippet.title: Rainbocorns Giant Egg Surprise Toy Unboxing #unboxingtoys #kids
snippet.description:
Rainbocorns Giant Egg Surprise Toy Unboxing

Ruby had so much fun with all these awesome rainbocorns kindly sent to us from Zuru toys! The giant egg was full with all the new rainbocorns including Wild heart surprise, sparkle heart surprise and itzy glitzy surprise, we unboxed one of each for our video and there was so many surprises in them including slime, stampers, Boo-Boocorns and fake nails! Ruby loved the elephantcorn as that was the one she had asked for! the little owl is also so cute! Thankyou Zuru toys! WE LOVE THEM.

ainbocorns Wild Heart Surprise Series 3 are full with totally WILD surprises! There are 10 layers of surprise including new wild Rainbocorn characters and the most Wild surprises yet! There are 6 new characters to collect including the new Tucancorn, Zebracorn and even a rare sparkle Slothcorn! Clip their sequin heart to their belly and flip their sequins to reveal what your character loves! Discover even more surprises like nail decals and Rainbocorn wild poop! There are new long tailed Boo-boocorns to collect, including rare twin Boo-Boocorns! Who will you find??

Hatch open the Itzy Glitzy surprise eggs to meet the new Itzy Glitzy Rainbocorns and all their glitzy surprises! There are 26 Itzy Glitzy characters to collect, including the rare golden unicorn and silver flamingocorn! The Itzy Glitzy’s come with so many surprises, including hair clips, rings, bows, wings and pop and swap heart gems! Your Itzy Gltizy character can even be used as a pencil topper! Mix and match the wings and heart between your Itzy Glitzy’s and ring, and collect and swap them all! Who will you find?!

Unbox a sparkly surprise with the new rainbocorns sparkle heart. Each mini rainbow comes with a sparkly heart that you can peel to reveal a hidden surprise! Every heart shows what your rainbow loves…what will you reveal?! these soft and cuddly rainbocorns come with all new colour changing boo-boocorns, just dip them in cold water and they transform before your eyes! There’s also gooey rainbocorn poop hiding in the egg that you can stretch and squeeze! Collect all 6 including puppycorn, kittycorn, flamingocorn, unicorn, LLAMACORN and bunnycorn
